overview: The Midwest region of the US indie circuits has never been hotter, and right now the Chicago area is one of the top locations in the scene, with AAW Pro, Freelance Wrestling, GALLI Lucha, Zelo Pro Wrestling, Pro Wrestling ZERO1 USA and much more. Warrior Wrestling is one of the younger promotions, rising up in the Spring of 2018, but it’s made an impression quick, combining the best in area wrestlers alongside some national and international powerhouses. That trend continues on Saturday night with Warrior Wrestling 8, which will feature two War of Attrition matches, one for the Women’s Championship and one for the Warrior Heavyweight Championship. You can watch Warrior Wrestling 8
title: Warrior Wrestling 8
